ie richtet ihren Blick somit nicht nur auf den Fußball im Deutschen Kaiserreich, sondern zugleich auf das Kaiserreich selbst.  aKing football before its reign: a historical study on the question of how football became acceptable in imperial Germany.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aPhysical education and trainingzGermanyxHistory. 0aSoccerzGermanyxHistory. 0aSports and statezGermanyxHistoryy19th century. 4aDeutsches Kaiserreich. 4aFußball. 4aGeschichtswissenschaft. 4aKulturgeschichte. 4aKörper. 4aKörpergeschichte. 4aSport. 4aSportwissenschaft. 4aSubjekt. 7aHISTORY / Social History.2bisacsh  aBody.  aCultural History.  aGerman Empire.  aHistory of the Body.  aSoccer.  aSport Science.  aSport.  aSubject.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2016z9783110485332oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPP Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070099208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839432372zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839432372423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839432372/original  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  a978-3-11-070099-2  PP Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2016  aZDB-23-DSWb2016  aZDB-23-TGPc2014d2016